PrecisOrder (a) consenting to the exercise by the PROVINCE OF SASKATCHEWAN of its statutory power to acquire an interest in some 35 hectares of land on LA PLONGE INDIAN RESERVE NO. 192, in Saskatchewan, for public highway and utility purposes, and (b) authorizing the transfer to the Province of administration and control of those lands for those purposes, in lieu of exercising those powers.
